title: adidas Skateboarding SF Seconds Feature
description:
Leftover footage from the San Francisco campaign shoot in September 2009 with Mark Gonzales, Dennis Busenitz, Silas Baxter-Neal, Tim O'Connor, Pete Eldridge, Benny Fairfax, Dave Bachinsky, Nestor Judkins, Lem Villemin, Vince del Valle and Jake Donnelly. 
Official Website: http://www.adidas.com/skateboarding
 Store Locator: http://bit.ly/qIFMfO
